data.description: NEW HVAC unit in 2019 w/ recent inspection receipts. WELL MAINTAINED 2bed/2bath + Den located on a cul-de-sac lot in the GATED active adult GOLF community: Solera by Del Webb. Open floor plan w/ large living area + separate dining area & neutral paint throughout. The Den/Study features French Doors off the living room w/ ample natural light. Kitchen features matching stainless steel appliances, pantry, staggered cabinetry, and breakfast nook. FRIDGE, WASH/DRYER all stay! Owners Suite features full bath w/ dual sinks, separate tub & shower + spacious walk-in closet. **AGE RESTRICTION WAIVER may be available via HOA**. Community Amenities: Fitness Center, bocce ball, heated pool/spa, library, billiard room, card room, kitchen, community offices and SO MUCH MORE!
